1
00:01:37,681 --> 00:01:38,241
Why is it just you here?

2
00:01:39,320 --> 00:01:40,320
The boss took leave,

3
00:01:41,601 --> 00:01:42,921
and dumped a pile of work on me.

4
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:44,680
Leave?

5
00:01:45,681 --> 00:01:46,561
Even with a bad cold,

6
00:01:46,601 --> 00:01:47,961
Jiang Anlan still insists on working.

7
00:01:48,761 --> 00:01:50,641
Su Wen wants his lecture attendees
to take photos.

8
00:01:51,001 --> 00:01:52,241
He asks them to photograph
their loved ones.

9
00:01:52,601 --> 00:01:54,161
He even asked the boss’s wife
to be his model.

10
00:01:54,721 --> 00:01:55,761
The boss is super protective
of his wife.

11
00:01:56,321 --> 00:01:56,801
Now,

12
00:01:57,081 --> 00:01:58,441
he’s sticking by her side,
won’t leave for a second.

13
00:02:01,441 --> 00:02:03,121
Didn’t expect Su Wen
to really fall for her.

14
00:02:03,641 --> 00:02:04,201
I think

15
00:02:04,841 --> 00:02:05,561
Anlan’s in trouble now.

16
00:02:06,641 --> 00:02:08,281
Su Wen’s no match
for the boss.

17
00:02:11,001 --> 00:02:12,121
Don’t you know Su Wen
has only ever loved

18
00:02:12,161 --> 00:02:13,201
one woman in his life?

19
00:02:13,841 --> 00:02:14,761
Are you kidding?

20
00:02:15,441 --> 00:02:17,801
He’s photographed
over a thousand models.

21
00:02:19,241 --> 00:02:21,881
I mean the leading lady
in his personal work.

22
00:02:22,481 --> 00:02:23,481
There’s only ever been one.

23
00:02:23,761 --> 00:02:24,161
Cuixi.

24
00:02:26,281 --> 00:02:26,721
Cuixi.

25
00:02:28,601 --> 00:02:30,961
Heard they had a love
that left a deep mark.

26
00:02:31,481 --> 00:02:32,961
Su Wen used to be
a caring, devoted guy.

27
00:02:33,681 --> 00:02:35,321
He got hurt too badly
in that relationship.

28
00:02:35,681 --> 00:02:37,281
That’s why he became
a playboy.

29
00:02:38,841 --> 00:02:40,881
What did Cuixi do

30
00:02:41,201 --> 00:02:42,361
to hurt Su Wen so much?

31
00:02:44,001 --> 00:02:44,881
That, I don’t know.

32
00:02:45,361 --> 00:02:45,961
Anyway,

33
00:02:46,241 --> 00:02:47,921
Yao Yuan is the second woman
after Cuixi

34
00:02:48,401 --> 00:02:49,721
that Su Wen has photographed.

35
00:02:50,121 --> 00:02:50,721
That means

36
00:02:51,961 --> 00:02:53,161
he’s serious this time.

37
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:10,560
Ugh, I’m really not used
to being a model.

38
00:03:11,521 --> 00:03:12,441
This feels way too awkward.

39
00:03:13,881 --> 00:03:16,081
My girlfriend’s beautiful,
even when she’s awkward.

40
00:03:17,161 --> 00:03:17,641
Old Jiang,

41
00:03:18,441 --> 00:03:20,601
your gear is already
a step behind mine.

42
00:03:21,161 --> 00:03:22,121
Mine’s professional grade.

43
00:03:22,761 --> 00:03:23,801
Yours is just amateur stuff.

44
00:03:24,961 --> 00:03:27,401
Back in middle school,
I used a point-and-shoot

45
00:03:27,441 --> 00:03:28,721
and still won first prize
in the city.

46
00:03:29,241 --> 00:03:30,481
If I got serious,

47
00:03:31,001 --> 00:03:32,241
you’d be out of a job.

48
00:03:33,841 --> 00:03:34,761
You two can’t go
even one minute

49
00:03:34,801 --> 00:03:36,201
without bickering, huh?

50
00:03:46,521 --> 00:03:47,161
By the way, Su Wen,

51
00:03:48,561 --> 00:03:50,081
I’ve always wanted
to ask you something.

52
00:03:51,521 --> 00:03:52,601
Why did you choose

53
00:03:53,041 --> 00:03:54,241
“loved one” as your theme
this time?

54
00:04:00,121 --> 00:04:00,761
Isn’t it because of you?

55
00:04:02,521 --> 00:04:04,001
Aren’t you just mixing
business with pleasure?

56
00:04:05,121 --> 00:04:06,481
Am I that fake?

57
00:04:09,121 --> 00:04:11,121
Didn’t you tell me
to find my original passion?

58
00:04:11,641 --> 00:04:13,321
That’s why I picked
this theme.

59
00:04:16,161 --> 00:04:17,401
When I started out,
I was broke.

60
00:04:22,041 --> 00:04:22,561
It was tough.

61
00:04:23,840 --> 00:04:25,080
I had to borrow money
from friends

62
00:04:25,521 --> 00:04:26,521
just to afford rent.

63
00:04:27,681 --> 00:04:29,241
But I was really happy
back then.

64
00:04:30,081 --> 00:04:30,561
I felt blessed.

65
00:04:31,641 --> 00:04:32,281
It’s because

66
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:39,240
people always wear masks
in life.

67
00:04:40,081 --> 00:04:40,921
Only in front of a loved one

68
00:04:41,241 --> 00:04:42,081
can you be your true self.

69
00:04:43,481 --> 00:04:44,801
Like a child,

70
00:04:45,401 --> 00:04:46,961
being willful, throwing tantrums,

71
00:04:47,241 --> 00:04:47,921
acting unreasonable.

72
00:04:52,721 --> 00:04:53,081
People

73
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:54,400
only show their true emotions

74
00:04:54,441 --> 00:04:56,121
in front of their loved one.

75
00:04:56,921 --> 00:04:57,761
That’s when you live
with real passion.

76
00:05:00,601 --> 00:05:02,201
That’s why I chose
this theme.

77
00:05:02,801 --> 00:05:04,281
When the loved one is present,

78
00:05:04,881 --> 00:05:06,521
the person in front of the lens
shows

79
00:05:06,561 --> 00:05:07,361
their truest side.

80
00:05:09,361 --> 00:05:10,881
Isn’t that what I,
as a photographer,

81
00:05:11,081 --> 00:05:11,961
want to capture most?

82
00:05:18,721 --> 00:05:20,121
That’s my self-analysis done.

83
00:05:21,321 --> 00:05:22,561
I have a question
for you too.

84
00:05:24,361 --> 00:05:25,241
Who do you want
to photograph?

85
00:05:30,081 --> 00:05:30,721
My grandma.

86
00:05:33,681 --> 00:05:34,401
Grandma?

87
00:05:36,801 --> 00:05:39,801
My grandma is the person
I love most in this world.

88
00:06:07,001 --> 00:06:09,041
I’m going to her place
this weekend.

89
00:06:09,521 --> 00:06:10,281
I’ll take some photos
of her.

90
00:06:12,641 --> 00:06:13,041
Mm-hmm.

91
00:06:15,441 --> 00:06:16,081
What’s wrong?

92
00:06:16,601 --> 00:06:18,121
You’ve been quiet
for a while.

93
00:06:26,081 --> 00:06:26,761
What’s up?

94
00:06:29,041 --> 00:06:29,601
It’s nothing.

95
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:31,760
I just want to hold you
for a bit.

96
00:06:32,761 --> 00:06:33,521
Just for a moment.

97
00:06:46,361 --> 00:06:47,001
I’m a little tired.

98
00:06:47,681 --> 00:06:48,481
I’ll stay out here.

99
00:06:48,881 --> 00:06:49,561
You should rest early.

100
00:06:52,481 --> 00:06:52,841
Okay.

101
00:06:54,721 --> 00:06:55,081
Go ahead.

102
00:07:31,121 --> 00:07:31,921
Boss, stop worrying about it.

103
00:07:32,801 --> 00:07:34,241
Your wife only ever has eyes for you.

104
00:07:34,881 --> 00:07:35,561
That Su Wen...

105
00:07:35,681 --> 00:07:37,001
will be out of the picture soon.

106
00:07:38,801 --> 00:07:40,881
I've never paid any attention to him.

107
00:07:43,041 --> 00:07:43,721
So you...

108
00:07:46,881 --> 00:07:48,721
Yao Yuan is going home to see her grandma this weekend.

109
00:07:50,241 --> 00:07:51,161
You want to go with her,

110
00:07:51,881 --> 00:07:53,641
but you're afraid her grandma will recognize you.

111
00:07:54,761 --> 00:07:55,801
Even if you don't go this time,

112
00:07:56,601 --> 00:07:58,041
you'll run into her eventually.

113
00:08:00,961 --> 00:08:02,041
How long has it been since that happened?

114
00:08:02,441 --> 00:08:03,721
Her grandma is getting old.

115
00:08:04,121 --> 00:08:04,841
She probably forgot.

116
00:08:05,961 --> 00:08:06,961
How could she possibly forget?

117
00:08:09,481 --> 00:08:09,801
Boss,

118
00:08:10,681 --> 00:08:12,241
it's really not your fault.

119
00:08:12,961 --> 00:08:14,681
You don't need to take all the blame.

120
00:08:17,681 --> 00:08:19,481
Your wife is reasonable too.

121
00:08:20,041 --> 00:08:21,361
You should talk to her when you get a chance.

122
00:08:21,921 --> 00:08:22,561
She'll understand you.

123
00:08:25,081 --> 00:08:25,361
Mm.

124
00:08:26,161 --> 00:08:27,801
Getting fussed over by two big shots all day—

125
00:08:27,841 --> 00:08:29,081
it was quite an experience.

126
00:08:30,241 --> 00:08:31,761
It's just two kids bickering.

127
00:08:31,801 --> 00:08:32,921
I have to keep mediating.

128
00:08:33,680 --> 00:08:34,480
On one side,

129
00:08:34,521 --> 00:08:35,761
is a talented, romantic,

130
00:08:35,801 --> 00:08:37,961
funny, popular artist.

131
00:08:38,560 --> 00:08:39,480
On the other side,

132
00:08:39,521 --> 00:08:40,841
is a rich, handsome guy admired by many actresses,

133
00:08:40,881 --> 00:08:43,641
but he's only devoted to you.

134
00:08:43,921 --> 00:08:44,601
If it were you,

135
00:08:44,761 --> 00:08:45,441
who would you choose?

136
00:08:46,961 --> 00:08:48,281
You bystander,

137
00:08:48,641 --> 00:08:49,561
enjoying the drama, huh?

138
00:08:51,241 --> 00:08:51,841
By the way,

139
00:08:52,241 --> 00:08:54,681
Su Wen may seem a bit roguish,

140
00:08:54,841 --> 00:08:56,361
but he's really devoted to you.

141
00:09:00,401 --> 00:09:02,361
You... you haven't fallen for him, have you?

142
00:09:05,521 --> 00:09:07,241
I just admire him, honestly.

143
00:09:07,680 --> 00:09:09,200
I think his work is excellent.

144
00:09:09,601 --> 00:09:10,961
It has nothing to do with feelings.

145
00:09:11,401 --> 00:09:12,401
Then why are you bothered?

146
00:09:13,641 --> 00:09:14,601
It's Jiang Anlan.

147
00:09:15,761 --> 00:09:16,601
I think

148
00:09:16,641 --> 00:09:17,881
he was acting strange today.

149
00:09:18,441 --> 00:09:19,761
Someone's after his girl—

150
00:09:19,801 --> 00:09:21,081
of course he's acting weird.

151
00:09:21,441 --> 00:09:23,721
He's probably so jealous right now,

152
00:09:24,201 --> 00:09:25,801
it's flooding the Yangtze and Yellow Rivers.

153
00:09:25,841 --> 00:09:27,641
Stop, that's not what I meant.

154
00:09:27,921 --> 00:09:29,081
It's not about jealousy.

155
00:09:29,121 --> 00:09:30,841
I just think he has something on his mind.

156
00:09:31,601 --> 00:09:34,081
He always seems mysterious anyway.

157
00:09:34,601 --> 00:09:35,601
Alright, stop worrying.

158
00:09:35,641 --> 00:09:36,881
Come play a dungeon run with me.

159
00:09:38,161 --> 00:09:38,561
I'm tired.

160
00:09:39,041 --> 00:09:39,441
I'm going to bed.

161
00:09:39,481 --> 00:09:40,281
You play by yourself.

162
00:09:41,361 --> 00:09:42,881
Yangtze, Yellow River...

163
00:09:47,041 --> 00:09:47,721
Alright.

164
00:09:51,961 --> 00:09:54,841
Where did all the Baihua Tang girls go?

165
00:09:55,201 --> 00:09:56,561
Li Xiaoya isn't online either.

166
00:09:57,481 --> 00:09:59,401
Is she still mad at me?

167
00:10:13,401 --> 00:10:14,681
If something's bothering you,

168
00:10:14,961 --> 00:10:15,841
don't keep it to yourself.

169
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:17,600
If you want to talk,

170
00:10:18,081 --> 00:10:18,801
I'm always here.

171
00:10:34,841 --> 00:10:35,241
It's nothing.

172
00:11:01,081 --> 00:11:01,881
Wen Ruyu.

173
00:11:39,961 --> 00:11:40,681
Why are you alone?

174
00:11:41,641 --> 00:11:42,881
Everyone at Baihua Tang is busy.

175
00:11:42,921 --> 00:11:43,721
Can't I come alone?

176
00:11:45,001 --> 00:11:45,841
You could've called me.

177
00:11:48,041 --> 00:11:48,921
What are you doing?

178
00:11:52,521 --> 00:11:53,201
We're even now.

179
00:11:54,401 --> 00:11:54,881
Hey, you—

180
00:12:07,241 --> 00:12:08,201
logging off just like that?

181
00:12:19,521 --> 00:12:20,681
Who could it be this late?

182
00:12:28,161 --> 00:12:29,481
Why are you here so late?

183
00:12:30,001 --> 00:12:30,961
Are you avoiding me?

184
00:12:31,721 --> 00:12:32,641
Why would I avoid you?

185
00:12:33,521 --> 00:12:34,641
Ever since last time we...

186
00:12:36,921 --> 00:12:37,401
Last time—

187
00:12:38,081 --> 00:12:38,841
Truth or Dare.

188
00:12:39,041 --> 00:12:39,761
You didn't finish your answer.

189
00:12:40,361 --> 00:12:42,321
I asked who you last kissed.

190
00:12:43,001 --> 00:12:44,041
Why did you look uncomfortable?

191
00:12:44,560 --> 00:12:46,120
You came just to ask me that?

192
00:12:47,001 --> 00:12:49,281
You think I analyze love on my show

193
00:12:49,321 --> 00:12:50,761
because I know it all?

194
00:12:51,001 --> 00:12:52,121
I've just heard a lot of stories,

195
00:12:52,161 --> 00:12:53,361
collected a lot of material.

196
00:12:53,721 --> 00:12:54,761
I don't want to be your material.

197
00:12:54,801 --> 00:12:55,281
Find someone else.

198
00:12:56,560 --> 00:12:58,600
If your mistakes can help others,

199
00:12:59,161 --> 00:13:00,321
that's a good thing.

200
00:13:04,721 --> 00:13:05,841
Two people meet,

201
00:13:06,041 --> 00:13:07,641
and over time, feelings fade.

202
00:13:07,921 --> 00:13:08,961
It ends quietly.

203
00:13:09,481 --> 00:13:10,721
Or one cheats,

204
00:13:11,121 --> 00:13:12,481
and they never speak again.

205
00:13:13,041 --> 00:13:14,601
Even if they grow old together,

206
00:13:15,361 --> 00:13:17,841
death will separate them someday.

207
00:13:18,161 --> 00:13:19,641
Isn't that just how relationships are?

208
00:13:21,201 --> 00:13:22,241
Your last relationship—

209
00:13:22,281 --> 00:13:23,561
how badly did it hurt you?

210
00:13:24,481 --> 00:13:25,681
The deeper the hurt,

211
00:13:26,481 --> 00:13:27,441
the more you resist love.

212
00:13:28,001 --> 00:13:29,641
Stop using your theories on me.

213
00:13:32,401 --> 00:13:33,241
The other person cheated.

214
00:13:34,921 --> 00:13:36,721
I don't want to talk about this. Good night.

215
00:13:38,241 --> 00:13:39,121
Don't you want them to see

216
00:13:39,161 --> 00:13:40,441
you're doing better than before,

217
00:13:40,801 --> 00:13:41,441
prettier,

218
00:13:41,801 --> 00:13:42,481
more confident?

219
00:13:43,560 --> 00:13:44,560
Don't you want him to regret it?

220
00:13:46,201 --> 00:13:47,041
Childish.

221
00:13:47,881 --> 00:13:48,961
They're getting married.

222
00:13:51,321 --> 00:13:52,841
He's marrying the one he cheated with.

223
00:13:56,401 --> 00:13:56,761
Yeah.

224
00:13:57,641 --> 00:13:58,681
He was my first love.

225
00:13:58,881 --> 00:14:00,801
My first relationship crushed me.

226
00:14:01,081 --> 00:14:02,481
I'm a loser in love.

227
00:14:02,521 --> 00:14:03,601
I'm just that useless.

228
00:14:03,641 --> 00:14:04,761
Happy with that answer?

229
00:14:06,721 --> 00:14:07,081
Xinran.

230
00:14:08,241 --> 00:14:09,521
Then you should go.

231
00:14:11,281 --> 00:14:12,121
When's the wedding?

232
00:14:12,641 --> 00:14:13,161
Where is it?

233
00:14:13,841 --> 00:14:14,601
I'll go with you.

234
00:14:17,241 --> 00:14:17,841
Hawaii.

235
00:14:19,121 --> 00:14:19,521
Ah.

236
00:14:20,281 --> 00:14:21,081
That's extravagant.

237
00:14:23,601 --> 00:14:24,041
But...

238
00:14:24,281 --> 00:14:25,121
Before the wedding,

239
00:14:25,881 --> 00:14:27,321
there's a class reunion.

240
00:14:29,121 --> 00:14:30,841
It's a perfect chance from above.

241
00:14:48,601 --> 00:14:51,561
Please look after Baihua Tang these days.

242
00:14:54,121 --> 00:14:54,561
Okay.

243
00:14:55,721 --> 00:14:56,881
Take care of yourself.

244
00:14:59,361 --> 00:15:00,561
Too bad I have work.

245
00:15:01,561 --> 00:15:03,041
I can't go with you.

246
00:15:04,681 --> 00:15:05,201
It's fine.

247
00:15:05,801 --> 00:15:06,481
Work comes first.

248
00:15:13,881 --> 00:15:15,161
Yao Yuan, let me go home with you.

249
00:15:22,321 --> 00:15:23,281
I'm going to my grandma's.

250
00:15:24,121 --> 00:15:24,921
I know.

251
00:15:25,721 --> 00:15:27,281
Home is where everyone belongs.

252
00:15:27,561 --> 00:15:28,521
Only when you return home

253
00:15:28,561 --> 00:15:29,721
can you truly relax.

254
00:15:29,761 --> 00:15:30,241
Feel at ease.

255
00:15:30,841 --> 00:15:32,241
I believe when you're home,

256
00:15:32,561 --> 00:15:33,441
you must feel especially relaxed.

257
00:15:34,361 --> 00:15:36,721
So I want to capture that with my camera.

258
00:15:44,041 --> 00:15:45,161
You can't control that, can you?

259
00:15:47,921 --> 00:15:49,401
Go wherever you want.

260
00:15:49,921 --> 00:15:50,961
That's your freedom.

261
00:15:52,001 --> 00:15:54,641
But if you cross the line,

262
00:15:56,001 --> 00:15:56,961
I absolutely—

263
00:16:04,881 --> 00:16:05,521
Jiang Anlan.

264
00:16:06,481 --> 00:16:08,881
You can only show off in the game.

265
00:16:24,721 --> 00:16:25,081
Yao Yuan.

266
00:16:25,561 --> 00:16:28,001
You look much better after coming home.

267
00:16:28,041 --> 00:16:29,361
Even your expression is more relaxed.

268
00:16:30,361 --> 00:16:30,801
Of course.

269
00:16:31,281 --> 00:16:31,801
I'm home, after all.

270
00:16:33,521 --> 00:16:35,481
By the way, I agreed to bring you this time

271
00:16:35,521 --> 00:16:36,561
because I respect

272
00:16:37,161 --> 00:16:38,921
the theme of the shoot.

273
00:16:39,241 --> 00:16:40,001
Got it?

274
00:16:40,761 --> 00:16:42,121
I'm a professional photographer.

275
00:16:42,161 --> 00:16:43,361
How could I not understand that?

276
00:16:44,441 --> 00:16:44,961
Good.

277
00:16:46,681 --> 00:16:47,041
Let me do it.

278
00:16:47,361 --> 00:16:48,761
Hey, I can handle it myself.

279
00:16:49,801 --> 00:16:50,761
We're going to your grandma's soon.

280
00:16:51,001 --> 00:16:52,761
If she sees you carrying your own luggage,

281
